### My Take

* **If your system will eventually support alumni access, longitudinal analysis, or multi-year reporting**, the **shed exos / archival relational approach** is more ‚Äúcorrect‚Äù and future-proof.
* **If your main goal is operational simplicity**, and you mostly care about JSON snapshots for reports/alumni, the **report-based approach** is enough and safer to implement now.

